1.title: A look back
1.plot: Jules sits down with actress Jennie Garth to learn why she LOVES the RV lifestyle and how she decorates her motor-home on a friendly budget. We meet former SF 49er Guy McIntyre and learn what inspires him to help children in the community.

2.title: RVing for every lifestyle & budget
2.plot: Jules Wilson travels to Las Vegas to check out the new Touring trailer. Jules and former SF 49er Guy McIntyre sit down at the home of former SF 49er Bubba Paris to see how RVing fits into his lifestyle and what he's doing to help others.

3.title: Latest, most innovative RV's
3.plot: In this episode, you'll discover awesome places to go RVing in Southern California, Jules and former SF 49er Guy McIntyre sit down with former Giant's manager Dusty Baker at SF hotspot, the Atwater Tavern and we'll showcase the latest and most innovative RVs. Ready, set, adventure!!.

4.title: RVing with SF 49er Joe Williams
4.plot: Jules Wilson takes us to meet with San Francisco 49er Joe Williams as he learns all about RVing, we also travel to the CA Rodeo Salinas, and we'll check out the vintage RV Retro with modern day conveniences.

5.title: Exciting Fall RVing
5.plot: Fall is one of the best times to go RVing. Join us as we showcase the "Outlaw" RV...is it a party machine, a Toy Hauler, or both? You'll also discover how fun it is to travel on an RV adventure to Ventura, CA.

1.title: Tailgating in style
1.plot: Tailgating at the San Francisco 49ers playoff game. What could be better? Tailgate in style with all of your friends in a diesel motorhome from See Grins RV. Game on!.

2.title: Rving at the water's edge
2.plot: Ever dream of vacationing right at the water's edge? We travel to Seascape Beach where you can RV and fall asleep to the sound of the ocean. Ahhh. How about a Landmark RV to take you there? All the luxurious comforts of your own home.

3.title: A "Man-cave" RV
3.plot: We take a trip to Casa De Fruita to experience the local RV fun. Before you go on your next trip, we show you how you can get there with a little "Attitude", or maybe you're a "Road Warrior" type of RVer and like to relax in your man-cave.

4.title: Is it a luxury suite or an RV?
4.plot: Why stay in a hotel when you can have your own luxury suite every time you travel in your Big Horn sky lounge model? Here at Seegrins we want to take care of all of your RV needs...check out the biggest RV Parts and Accessories department west of the Mississippi. All of this is waiting for you at Seegrins.

5.title: Discover the fun of "Dry Camping"
5.plot: We show you the fun and freedom of "Dry Camping", we take a look at our hot little Mavrics, we show you how much fun a toy hauler is, and we take you to Camp 49er RV Ranch where you can pan for gold.

6.title: Room for everyone
6.plot: The Wynn's take us to the San Francisco RV resort, and then we head east to Chesapeake Bay. With an Ultra-lite travel trailer, all you need is any small SUV to tow and you'll be on your way to making your own magic memories.

7.title: Bring all your toys in a Cyclone RV
7.plot: When we say, "Let's create great RV adventures", we mean it!' So, we took a little trip to Acadia, Maine. How about taking you own trip in a Cyclone RV? It's the perfect choice for taking all your toys on an amazing adventure.

8.title: With an RV pets are always welcome
8.plot: When you travel in an RV, you can bring your pets with you. Steve Folan shows us that Seegrins has the best selection of RVs For Sale By Owner like Fleetwood, Winnebago, Tiffin, Monaco and Newmar.

9.title: Take a walk down "5th wheel avenue"
9.plot: We'll show you how the "Element RV" is just like riding in your own private luxury jet...and don't we all deserve just a little bit of luxury?. We also show you how "fly fishing" is great for family bonding, and we take a walk down 5th wheel avenue.

1.title: You can RV all year long
1.plot: Here at See Grins, it really is an RV show everyday!. Enjoy free foods on the weekends, and we are always ready for a fun adventure. In this show we take you to Shaver Lake where you can RV ALL YEAR LONG.

2.title: Falling in love with RVing
2.plot: In this episode we travel to the Jersey Shore and experience the thrill of the Steel Pier. We spotlight a toy hauler that is "cooler" than an "Outlaw". How about a travel trailer that you can tow with your smaller SUV? Here at Seegrins, everyone is a VIP.

3.title: Health Benefits of RVing
3.plot: Did you know that there are actually health benefits to RVing for you and your family? Looking for some real adventure? How about hitting the road with a "Roadtrek". And, we'll take you to the largest water park in America!.

4.title: The "Gateway" to your RV Dreams
4.plot: In this fun-filled episode, we'll take you to one of the most popular RV resorts in the Bay Area. We'll also take you to the tallest lighthouse on the West Coast and show you where you can get up close and personal with the majestic elephant seals. We love a good challenge...Seegrins has been put to an RV challenge...can Seegrins deliver???

5.title: Meet a sexy Desert Fox
5.plot: Whether it's a sexy Desert Fox or a cute sleeping dog, here at See Grins RV, we love all kinds of animals. We also love fast-paced adventures and we'll take you to a place where you can experience the thrill of the checkered flag. Plus, we showcase the coolest innovative RV's to take you anywhere YOU want to go. On your mark...get set...GO!!.

6.title: RV Summer Time Fun
6.plot: No matter what your definition of fun and adventure is - Getting away from the city to find peace and tranquility, playing in the sand like a child again, or soaring to new heights; this episode is jam-packed with summer fun for all. And don't forget, folks, with an RV - the FUN never stops!

7.title: Solar-Powered RV's
7.plot: Seegrins is THE ONLY place to check out the diesel, solar powered "Roadrek". What a beauty that is good for the environment and your pocketbook. When you RV, healthy eating is easy, especially when your next RV adventure takes you to Casa De Fruta; which we visit in this fun-filled episode. We also take you to the wilderness...oops; we mean we showcase the beautiful Wilderness, Excursion and Coleman RV's. So fun!!.

8.title: Driving an RV is easy
8.plot: Life is filled with wonder and excitement ...it's what the "Good Life' is all about. Today we show you how EASY it is to drive a 40 foot diesel motorhome...no joke. The "Discovery": is easy to drive and so luxurious...all of the comforts of home. RVing is all about comfort and convenience. And, what do RV's have to do with the professional Dog Show world...we'll take you to Carmel, CA to find out!.

9.title: The Comforts of Home
9.plot: We all know there's no place like home. But, where do you stay when your call for adventure takes you away from home? And how do you bring the comforts of home with you? With an RV, you can enjoy comfort and ease in all your travels. We'll show you the latest and coolest RV's at the huge Seegrins RV show going on RIGHT NOW.

10.title: Rving Brings Freedom
10.plot: FREEDOM means being able to live life to the fullest. We show you how you can get your freedom back, so you can hit the road, and discover this beautiful country we call home. It's time to get off that couch.

1.title: Rving, Relaxing and Romance
1.plot: The New Year means new beginnings. An opportunity to spend more quality time with family and friends. A new chance for romance and more adventures, a resolution to make 2014 your best year ever. In this episode, it's all about new beginnings and having lots more fun.

2.title: Small, Mid-Size and Large Rv's
2.plot: How do you define adventure? Is it a cross-country trip or a fun weekend getaway just north of the Golden Gate Bridge? Maybe your sense of adventure is an adrenaline fix. We show you the best ways to travel to your favorite adventures.

3.title: RVing means no reservations required
3.plot: Spontaneity: the ability to take control of your life right when the desire grabs you. No reservations required, no early check-out, no packing. Adventures are just around the corner.

4.title: Spring-Time RVing
4.plot: "SPRINGTIME!" The sun is shining and this means you have more time to get outdoors and enjoy it. And there's no better way to enjoy Spring's treasures than with an RV. Plus, one of our viewers has put See Grins to the test.

5.title: The Best Iconic RV's
5.plot: It's that time of year to get your spring back in your step. The time when life around you awakens. Kids are dreaming of summer adventures, and the kid in you is ready for adventure, fun and romance. In this episode, you'll find many ways to get the spring back in your step.

6.title: A New Backyard Every Weekend
6.plot: The journey is truly the seasoning of life. Is this episode, you'll encounter unexpected treasures around every bend and you'll discover how to enjoy a new backyard every weekend. Plus, we showcase the latest and coolest iconic RV's.

7.title: The coolest tricked-out Toy Hauler
7.plot: The great outdoors is so close...it's just one adventurous road trip away. Whether it's being a part of nature in the great outdoors or being a part of an exciting event, how easy is it to take that journey? Let's discover together how fun RVing can be in this fun-filled episode of "RV with Me".

8.title: Tour the Winnebago Factory
8.plot: We take you to the Hollister Harley Rally. Another one of our viewers is putting See Grins RV to the test, we'll show you the best way to travel to Hollywood. And come join us on an exclusive tour of the fascinating Winnebago factory.

9.title: 3 Incredible Ways to Save
9.plot: Time to tailgate with family and friends, time to steal away for a fun weekend just the two of you...or the four of you. However you define "weekend", See Grins RV is here to help you make it unforgettable.

10.title: Fall and Winter RVing
10.plot: There are so many things to love about the fall and Winter Season. New fresh fallen leaves, the adventure you've always wanted to try that long overdue romantic get-away, falling in love with the open road and the great outdoors...and See Grins RV is here to help you make every season the Best It Can Be.

1.title: Biggest RV Show and Sale
1.plot: Come join us as we showcase the best RV's of 2015. Looking for an RV adventure? We'll take you to the No CA Renaissance Fair in Hollister, CA. And, See Grins is all about the iconic RVs: Lance, Coleman, Winnebago, to name just a few.

2.title: See Grins is the #1 Motorhome Dealership in CA!
2.plot: Love sports??? You'll discover how having an RV can make your hobbies even more enjoyable for the entire family, and See Grins RV is all about Good Vibrations. We'll introduce you to the best Beach Boys tribute band in the country.

3.title: Tour the Lance RV Factory
3.plot: Get ready for Springtime RV. In today's show, we're going to introduce you to an RV club that really knows how to celebrate life, no matter which season it is. You'll discover how easy it is to get into the RV lifestyle and, we're going to take you on an exclusive tour of the incredible Lance RV factory.

4.title: Biggest RV Show in NorCal!
4.plot: It's that time of year when life around us awakens. Now's the perfect time to get outside and have more fun with family and friends. At the biggest and best RV show going on right now, See Grins has the RV of your dreams. Come join us.

5.title: The RV of Your Dreams!
5.plot: There are so many incredible places to explore in this great country of ours. Just around the bend is where you'll find a chance for adventure, the gift of new birth, an opportunity for a return to romance. And with the best selection of RV's in all of Northern California, See Grins RV is here to help get you started.

6.title: RV Summer Spectacular
6.plot: It's Summertime. That special time of year when the days are LONGER and this means more time to create special memories with family and friends...and with an RV, you can enjoy the activities and adventures you love most when you travel.

7.title: RVing for Every Lifestyle
7.plot: Life is filed with possibilities, discovery and wonder around every bend. New possibilities for freedom, independence and discovering how easy it is to get closer to family in just one weekend.

8.title: An exciting RV daycation!
8.plot: Adventure...Romance...Excitement!!. It's all waiting just outside your door. And with an RV, the adventure begins the second you hit the road...and See Gins RV is here to help you get the adventures started.

9.title: RV Romance and Adventure!!!
9.plot: How do you define adventure? Is it a cross country trip discovering nature's wonders? Is it a long romantic weekend...just the two of you? Or, is it Game Day tailgating with family and friends? Adventure...Romance...Excitement!!.

10.title: RVing home for the Holidays!
10.plot: In this episode, we take you to the breathtaking ocean-front San Francisco RV Resort; and in Jules' RV Review, we showcase the gorgeous Navion by Winnebago...'tis the season for adventure and fun.

11.title: RV Travels with See Grins RV
11.plot: The holidays are all about family and friends. Spending more quality time together, new thrilling adventure and taking time for more fun and romance in your life. There's no better time to enjoy life to the fullest.

1.title: Largest RV Show and Sale - Happy New Year
1.plot: With an RV, you can create more special moments with family and friends, re-connect with nature, how about creating more ROMANCE in your life. With an RV, you take your home on the road and there's no limit to what you can discover.

2.title: Pechanga RV Resort Excitement!
2.plot: We travel to Temecula, CA and the Pechanga RV Resort. A first-class RV resort, Hot Air Ballooning, wine tasting, swimming, the casino. In Jules' RV Consumer review, find out what she likes best about the Big Country 5th Wheel by Heartland.

3.title: Best places to RV in CA!
3.plot: Join us as we take you to the best places to RV in CA. Jules Wilson also reviews the new Palazzo Motorhome in her "Consumer RV Review". This episode of "RV with Me" is jam-packed with RV fun, adventure and RV education.

4.title: RVing for Adventure!
4.plot: We take you to Laguna Seca for the Continental Monterey Grand Prix, the Hollister Bike Rally and Orange Grove RV Resort. Plus, we showcase the latest, innovative RV's, including Jules' RV Consumer Review. Get your engines started.

5.title: Hi-tech RVing!
5.plot: The California RV travel show that takes you to the best places to go RVing in California , along with exciting events and adventures you'll want to put in your travel list. Plus we showcase the latest and most Innovative RVs.

6.title: Fun places to go RVing
6.plot: Discover how the Big Country 5th Wheel is filled with luxury. Come with us as we travel to fun places to go RVing like Hearst Castle, and we'll show you how to sleep like a baby in your RV.

7.title: RVing with a SF 49er!
7.plot: RVing at Fort Bragg and Glass Beach, Jules RV Review of the Minnie by Winnebago and check out the new Scorpion Toy Hauler by Winnebago.

1.title: New Year, New You.
1.plot: Jules reviews the 2017 Riverstone 38RE by Forest River and we'll show you how to pull a 5th wheel, discover the luxurious live-aboard 2017 Tuscany 38SQ by Thor, and the 2017 Lance Travel Trailer 2155. Plus, an RV adventure to Death Valley.

2.title: Salton Sea Rving
2.plot: Your RV adventures begin at See Grins RV. Take an RV trip to the Salton Sea, discover the smaller Chateau motor-home, the lightweight Outback Travel trailer, and Jules reviews the luxurious 2017 Fleetwood Bounder.

3.title: Lake Havasu
3.plot: The California RV lifestyle show with the best places to go RVing and the latest RV's. Check out the Micro Minnie and the Minnie Winnie both by Winnebago, and an RV adventure to the London Bridge at Lake Havasu.

4.title: Ride 4 Life
4.plot: "RV with Me" is all about RV's, family and friendship. Check out the latest RVs, fun places to travel, and a "Ride 4 Life" weekend to help children and families in need.

5.title: Sea Otter Classic
5.plot: Come discover why RVing is becoming the most popular way to see the USA. Jules Wilson travels to the Subaru Sea Otter Classic in Monterey for lots of fun and adventure.

7.title: Vintage RV Rally
7.plot: Jules travels to the Vintage RV Rally for lots of fast paced adventure. And you'll discover the newest and most luxurious and innovative RVs made today. Plus, we learn from one very special family how RVing brings them true freedom.

8.title: Hollister Harley Rally
8.plot: Come discover why RVing is becoming the most popular way to see the USA. Jules Wilson travels to the Hollister Harley Rally for some fast paced fun.

9.title: Hollister Hills
9.plot: How to remodel your RV, motocross racing at Hollister Hills, RVing at Oceanside, CA and the Oceanside RV resort, Vintage RV camping, the smallest motor-home Jules Wilson has ever driven and lots more in this episode of "RV with Me".

10.title: Ghost Mountain
10.plot: We check out the 2018 Coachmen Prism, the 2017 Forest River Sonoma 270BHS, and the Solera Smart Arm Awning. Plus, Jules travels to Pollock Pines and the original sound stage of the old TV show, The Virginian.

imdb.plot outline: Rv with Me is All About Where to Go Rving, the Best Places to Travel, Family Fun, the Best Motorhomes, the Best Trailers, the Most Popular Toy Haulers, Featuring Both New Rvs and Used Rvs for Sale by Owners; Our Tv Host Jules Wilson Also Gives Consumer Reviews of Rvs.
